---

<section class="product-reviews padded" id="people">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-container center">
      <h2 class="h2-title">Built for teams that need a clean audit trail fast</h2>
      <p>
        Use AuditTrail for product changes, admin activity, exports, and the
        evidence you need when someone asks what happened and when.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="customer-reviews">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="one-half column">
          <div class="customer-card">
            <h4>
              “We replaced ad hoc spreadsheets with an actual product trail. The
              organization and project model makes it much easier to reason about.”
            </h4>
            <div class="bottom-card">
              <div class="circular-image">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3756985/pexels-photo-3756985.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Customer portrait">
              </div>
              <div>
                <h5>Marta, Product Ops</h5>
                <p>B2B SaaS team</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="one-half column">
          <div class="customer-card">
            <h4>
              “Exports are predictable, the auth flow is straightforward, and the
              dashboard matches what our auditors actually ask for.”
            </h4>
            <div class="bottom-card">
              <div class="circular-image">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3394657/pexels-photo-3394657.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Customer portrait">
              </div>
              <div>
                <h5>Daniel, Security Lead</h5>
                <p>Internal platform team</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
.customer-reviews{
  padding: 30px 0;
  h4{
    font-size: 2.3rem;
  }

  .customer-card{
    margin-top: 30px;
  }
}

.circular-image {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin-right: 10px;
    img{
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  .bottom-card{
    display: flex;
    padding: 10px 0;
    div:nth-child(2){
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
    h5, p{
      margin: 0px;
    }
    h5{
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  }
</style>
